   - 'source_hints': Keywords from the template to help the extractor locate this field.
   - 'content_expectation': What kind of content is expected (e.g., 'Action-oriented bullet points', 'A short paragraph').
   - 'structure_expectation': MUST be a plain descriptive string (e.g., 'Title on line 1 bold, Company | Location on line 2, bullet points below'). NEVER output an object like {"degree_name": "..."}.
   - 'constraints': MUST be a plain string describing limits (e.g., 'Max 5 bullet points'). NEVER an object.
   - 'ambiguity_note': (Optional) A plain string explaining any uncertainty. NEVER an object.
   - 'tag': The literal text of the marker as it appears in the template.
